## Workspace conventions

- PRDs → `Outputs/Product PRDs/YYYY-MM-DD_<short-slug>.md` (prefix the tracker key when known: `YYYY-MM-DD_<TRACKER-KEY>-<n>_<short-slug>.md`)
- Technical Design Docs → `Outputs/Technical Docs/`
- Learnings / retros (`/10-learn`) → `Learnings/`

